metadata.title: Mini Dishwasher, Portable Dishwasher Usb‑Powered With Suction Cup, Small Dish Washing Machine for Kitchen and Restaurant[White]
features: With a wide range of applications, it is very suitable for use in kitchens, restaurants and hotels. Compared with hand washing, it can improve efficiency and speed.
Small and compact, it can be directly placed in the basin to wash dishes, which is easy and convenient, saves time and effort, and avoids fatigue in the hand.
Automatic shutdown design, it can automatically shut down after 15 minutes of work, saving power and effort, safe and caring.

Efficient cleaning effect, it produces high‑speed vibration and high‑pressure water spray, which can accelerate the dispersion, emulsification and peeling of liquids and stains to achieve cleanliness.
Two modes, it uses wave‑making washing and super shock interactive dual cleaning mode, which can help you more thoroughly clear the stains on the bowl.

Automatic shutdown design, it can automatically shut down after 15 minutes of work, saving power and effort, safe and caring.How to Use:1. Drain water.2. Put in a bowl and add a small amount of detergent.3. One side of the suction cup sucks the bottom of the dishwasher.4. The other side of the suction cup sucks the wall of the sink.5. Plug in the power cord and start working.Specification:Item Type: DishwasherVoltage: 5VWeight: Approx. 351g / 12.4ozMaterial: ABSCurrent: 2APower: 14WSpeed: 12500 RpmWaterproof Rating: IP67Automatic Shutdown Time: After 15 Minutes Package List:1 x Dishwasher1 x Suction Cup1 x ManualNote:Please use a 5V‑2A adapter to power the product.
